<Layout title="Body Weight: Should You Track in kg or lbs?" description="Track body weight in kg or lbs? Compare precision, ease of tracking, and which unit works better for fitness goals." keywords="body weight kg or lbs, weight tracking, fitness weight, metric vs imperial weight, weight loss tracking, body weight measurement, scale units">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
